ETS' United Way Campaign is in full force.  To date, we've raised over $252,000, 60% of ETS' goal of $346,000.  
 
To the 73% of ETS employees who have logged on to the United Way pledge system, THANK YOU for your generosity.  
 
For the other 27%, please log on today to make a choice to contribute to the United Way.  It's quick and it's easy.  
 
Just log on to home.enron.com <http://home.enron.com/> and click on the United Way link on the left side of the home page.  If you have any trouble keying in your contribution, please contact Sarah Haden at x53383.
 
Employees who log on to the United Way pledge system and complete their on-line pledge by NOON on Thursday, August 16, will be eligible for a raffle drawing to be held at 1:00pm on Thursday. 
 
Included in the raffle drawing are 2 sets of Astros tickets for the 2002 season, 2 sets of Rockets tickets for the 2002 season and the grand prize of round-trip airline tickets for two (2) on Continental Airlines.
 
Don't miss out on this opportunity to win some great prizes!  Log on by NOON on Thursday, August 16, to be entered into the drawing.  
 
If you have questions about this year's campaign, please contact Gina Taylor at x37681.
 
The United Way helps so many people in our community in so many ways.  Please make your contribution today.  I think you'll be glad you did.
 
Stan